Package net.jawr.web.resource.bundle.global.processor

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ChainedGlobalProcessor<T extends AbstractGlobalProcessingContext>
    This interface is implemented by any object which can handle the chained global resource preprocessor.
    GlobalProcessor<T extends AbstractGlobalProcessingContext>
    This interface defines the interface for the global preprocessor.
    GlobalProcessorChainFactory<T extends AbstractGlobalProcessingContext>
    Interface for a factory of chained preprocessor objects.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractChainedGlobalProcessor<T extends AbstractGlobalProcessingContext>
    This class defines the abstract class for the preprocessor, which handle one type of resource bundle.
    AbstractGlobalProcessingContext
    This class defines the context for the global preprocessing
    AbstractGlobalProcessorChainFactory<T extends AbstractGlobalProcessingContext>
    This class defines the global preprocessor factory.
    CustomGlobalProcessorChainedWrapper<T extends AbstractGlobalProcessingContext>
    This class defines the wrapper, which wraps a custom global processor to a chained global processor.
    EmptyGlobalProcessor<T extends AbstractGlobalProcessingContext>
    This class defines the empty global preprocessor, which do nothing.
